Hey Guyz, Raffa here.

GENERAL DETAILS: 
The map was created in 3 days and may contain some gliches and minor flaws. (If you find any post and I will fix A.S.A.P)

This map was created because of inspiration from the COD4 map "showdown" (NOTE: This map is not copied and is different in many ways.) This map uses the general outline of Showdown but the detailed layout is very different. This map contains loads of good battle areas.

This map would not have been possible without constant advice and help from my good friend DoM. ( smucky_7 on fpsbanana.) I would also like to thank Golebi for hosting some tests. =D
